d":"IC_kwDOPUU0qc7-wwrl","user":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2026-04-18T17:13:23Z","updated_at":"2026-04-18T17:13:23Z","body":"## 🤖 Round 3: extracted Dockerfile inline node -e into [`scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs`](https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/blob/issue-1642-51e94ad4ccf4/scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs)\n\nCommit: `884311e1`. Addresses the latest review comment asking for a readable, maintainable, testable, deduplicated \\`.mjs\\` file that reuses src/ logic.\n\n### What changed\n\n**New file** [`scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs`](https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/blob/issue-1642-51e94ad4ccf4/scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs) — ~45 lines, fully reuses:\n- `ensureClaudeQuietConfig` from [`src/claude-quiet-config.lib.mjs`](https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/blob/issue-1642-51e94ad4ccf4/src/claude-quiet-config.lib.mjs)\n- `ensureDisallowedToolsInSettings` from [`src/useless-tools.lib.mjs`](https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/blob/issue-1642-51e94ad4ccf4/src/useless-tools.lib.mjs)\n\nNo key/value lists are duplicated — the script pulls everything from the shared \\`REQUIRED_CLAUDE_QUIET_ENV\\` / \\`REQUIRED_CLAUDE_QUIET_SETTINGS\\` / \\`REQUIRED_CLAUDE_QUIET_ATTRIBUTION\\` / \\`REQUIRED_CLAUDE_QUIET_PERMISSIONS\\` / \\`USELESS_CLAUDE_BUILTIN_TOOLS\\` / \\`USELESS_MCP_TOOL_NAME_PREFIXES\\` constants used by \\`solve\\` and all tests.\n\n**Dockerfile & coolify/Dockerfile** — replaced the ~25-line inline \\`node -e \\\"...\\\"\\` blob with:\n\n\\`\\`\\`dockerfile\nCOPY --chown=sandbox:sandbox \\\\\n    src/claude-quiet-config.lib.mjs \\\\\n    src/useless-tools.lib.mjs \\\\\n    /workspace/.hive-mind-bake/src/\nCOPY --chown=sandbox:sandbox \\\\\n    scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs \\\\\n    /workspace/.hive-mind-bake/scripts/\nRUN mkdir -p /workspace/.claude && \\\\\n    node /workspace/.hive-mind-bake/scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs \\\\\n        --settings-path /workspace/.claude/settings.json && \\\\\n    rm -rf /workspace/.hive-mind-bake\n\\`\\`\\`\n\nThe required 12 env vars are still set via \\`ENV\\` at image scope (separately from the script), so the container remains quiet even if \\`solve\\` is bypassed.\n\n**Tests updated**\n- \\`tests/test-claude-quiet-config.mjs\\` — Dockerfile assertions now verify it invokes the shared script and COPIES the two src libs. A new end-to-end block spawns \\`scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs\\` against a scratch \\`settings.json\\` and asserts every required env / settings / attribution / permissions / disallowedTools entry is present, plus idempotency on a second run.\n- \\`tests/useless-tools.test.mjs\\` — same Dockerfile indirection pattern for the disallowedTools assertions.\n\n### Verification\n\n- \\`node tests/test-claude-quiet-config.mjs\\` — passes\n- \\`node tests/useless-tools.test.mjs\\` — 22 passed, 0 failed\n- \\`npm test\\` — 41 passed, 0 failed\n- \\`npm run lint\\` — clean\n- \\`npm run format:check\\` — clean\n- \\`npm run check:duplication\\` — clean (10.51%, under 11% threshold)\n- \\`bash scripts/check-file-line-limits.sh\\` — clean\n- \\`bash scripts/check-mjs-syntax.sh\\` — clean\n- \\`node scripts/validate-changeset.mjs\\` — passes\n- \\`node tests/docs-validation.mjs\\` — passes\n- Simulated the Dockerfile steps locally by copying the 3 files into a scratch \\`/tmp\\` directory and running the script — produces an identical \\`settings.json\\` to the old inline \\`node -e\\` blob.\n\n### What stayed the same\n\n- Every required env var (12), settings key (10 top-level), \\`attribution\\` override (2), \\`permissions\\` override (1), and disallowedTools entry (16) from rounds 1–2 is still enforced.\n- \\`--dangerously-skip-permissions\\` is still passed on the CLI as belt-and-suspenders.\n- \\`getClaudeEnv()\\` still forces every required env var on every Claude subprocess.\n- \\`claude.lib.mjs#executeClaudeCommand()\\` still calls \\`ensureClaudeQuietConfig({ log })\\` immediately before launching Claude and logs the one-line summary.","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/comments/4274195173/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/comments/4274196022","html_url":"https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1643#issuecomment-4274196022","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/1643","id":4274196022,"node_id":"IC_kwDOPUU0qc7-ww42","user":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gist