[2026-04-18T17:27:57.271Z] [INFO]         "type": "tool_result",
[2026-04-18T17:27:57.271Z] [INFO]         "content": "I think even better if we set bin reusable command as part of Hive Mind package, so once we get if from latest NPM version for that we should build our docker image after we confirm the npm package is published. Name the command `configure-claude`, so it may be used by our users and system administrators to reset claude code configuration and verify it, so there will be no need to copy files to Dockerfiles themselves, once Hive Mind package with new command is installed. That way it will be useful and reusable for both docker and manually by our users.",
[2026-04-18T17:27:57.271Z] [INFO]         "is_error": false
[2026-04-18T17:27:57.271Z] [INFO]       }
[2026-04-18T17:27:57.271Z] [INFO]     ]
