[2026-04-18T17:44:02.204Z] [INFO]         "text": "Shipped `configure-claude` as a reusable bin in [commit `39657540`](https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1643/commits/39657540) addressing the round-4 maintainer ask. PR is now MERGEABLE + CLEAN on main.\n\n**What landed:**\n- `src/configure-claude.mjs` (bin entry) + `src/configure-claude.lib.mjs` (shared runner with `runConfigureClaude`, `verifyConfigureClaude`, arg parsing, help text)\n- `configure-claude` registered in `package.json` `bin` + `build:pre`; installable via `bun install -g @link-assistant/hive-mind`\n- `scripts/configure-claude-quiet-defaults.mjs` collapsed to a thin delegate so Dockerfile, CLI, and tests share one code path\n- Both Dockerfiles now also COPY `src/configure-claude.lib.mjs` and document that the bin is on PATH post-install\n- New `tests/test-configure-claude-bin.mjs` (wired into `npm test`) covers apply, `--verify` success/drift, idempotency, `--help`, and the package.json contract\n- Changeset amended to describe the new bin\n\n**Verification:** all local checks clean (lint, format, duplication 10.51%, line-limits, docs-validation); CI green (test-suites, test-execution, docker-pr-check, lint, memory-check, helm-pr-check all success). PR #1643: https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1643"
